'''TorrentFreak''' is a [[weblog]] dedicated to reporting the latest news on the [[BitTorrent (protocol)|BitTorrent]] protocol filesharing. TorrentFreak was started in November 2005 by a [[Dutch people|Dutch]]man named Ernesto.<ref>[http://uscpwned.blogspot.com/2007/05/final-project-interview-2-ernesto-of.html Pwned: Final Project Interview #2: Ernesto of TorrentFreak.com<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> He added Smaran to his staff in September 2006, as well as Enigmax in February 2007.<ref>[http://torrentfreak.com/about/ About | TorrentFreak<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
